## Accessibility (a11y)

### WCAG Guidelines

**Level A (Minimum):**
- Text alternatives for images
- Keyboard accessible
- Sufficient color contrast
- Proper heading structure

**Level AA (Target):**
- 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text
- 3:1 for large text
- No information by color alone
- Resizable text up to 200%

**Level AAA (Enhanced):**
- 7:1 contrast ratio
- No images of text
- Enhanced error suggestions

